 mọi khó khăn trở ngại, Dao Nuea và Nai đã giải quyết vấn đề của riêng mình và đến với nhau. Xem Check Out Series - Đêm Đó Cùng Cậu Sao Bắc Đẩu Vietsub sớm nhất trên iQiyi và iQ.com. Lịch chiếu phim Check Out và Review phim Check Out sẽ sớm được cập nhật.</p>","tmdb_id":130469,"cast":["Chahub Marut Ghoummeddin","Vittawin Veeravidhayanant","Boat Anakame Binsaman","M Sarawut Laoruamsap","Beam Atichart Lawansathian","Korravee Keawko","Sirilapas Kongtrakarn"],"director":["Kapper Worarit Ninklom"],"keywords":[],"tmdb":{"type":"tv","id":"130469","season":1,"vote_average":4.8,"vote_count":10},"cast_meta":[{"name":"Chahub Marut Ghoummeddin","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Chahub Marut Ghoummeddin","tmdb_id":3099664,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/7CQUznE0LzJJu3FKJarwOFhpq84.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3099664"},{"name":"Vittawin Veeravidhayanant","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Vittawin Veeravidhayanant","tmdb_id":2098569,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/i61i9HdL6WZm4ThG9clrhetUOaz.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/2098569"},{"name":"Boat Anakame Binsaman","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Boat Anakame Binsaman","tmdb_id":3291080,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/x4oZxTVE05U111a7w3LpEXGTKaj.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3291080"},{"name":"M Sarawut Laoruamsap","name_vi":null,"name_original":"M Sarawut Laoruamsap","tmdb_id":3291081,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/Aluv4SdGnepo22zczM9RTU1vCbw.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3291081"},{"name":"Beam Atichart Lawansathian","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Beam Atichart Lawansathian","tmdb_id":3680379,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/aCKEmWnPtmVqgTopUur2fPboCWk.jpg","tmdb_url":"https://www.themoviedb.org/person/3680379"},{"name":"Korravee Keawko","name_vi":null,"name_original":"Korravee Keawko","tmdb_id":2889095,"profile":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/enN6N9tlkfo2U76FCL2mh0xV4Qx.jpg","tmdb_url":"https: